Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.58,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}海
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:10.00,AIR Title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,830)}{\fad(1000,0)}青   空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:18.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我夢到了一個非常喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:29.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}往人他  最終還是回到我身邊了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:32.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還告訴了我一些重要的事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:37.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以  我不能就這樣放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:41.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係  我一個人也可以努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:23.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天去外邊走走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然走路還感覺有些辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我試著努力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}稍稍休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:45.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到頭來  還是要喝這個奇怪的果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直和我們生活在一起的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:02:59.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.69,0:03:04.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像似曾相識
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個吃閒飯的傢伙走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}反正他要是找不到落腳的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:15.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到時候就會返回這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也很辛苦的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.54,0:03:22.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一直為了能讓觀鈴留在神尾家而努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}終有一天會被帶回橘他們家去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:31.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然和你一起生活但卻無法照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為如果喜歡上你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}分別的時候會很傷心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直以平靜的心情等待著分別那天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過看來是沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經無法再欺騙自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:50.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓你成為我家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我一直跪在橘他們家門口求他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:55.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}最後他們拗不過我就答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經決定了一個人努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}決定了不給其他人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:08.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:10.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你怎麼了  觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:16.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原來你病得這麼重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我本以為只是熱傷風而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腳動不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去看醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一定可以治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:31.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對了  去找那個診所的女大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:33.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一定會幫助我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}去醫院也是治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我與往人一起找到了病因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}天空中有另外一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:46.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人一直背負著些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:50.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因此我的身體才漸漸地不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}總是說些天方夜譚似的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:05:00.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像以往一樣  我們繼續互不干涉的生活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:03.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}兩個人各自活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會一個人努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說  說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是因為一直沒關懷過你所以生我的氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:16.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不想去醫院也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會好好照顧你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過兩個人總比一個人好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:26.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們兩個人一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:27.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好嗎  觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:36.79,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼樣  好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.01,0:05:43.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}下回會做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽做的飯總是很難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}孩子可也都是吃父母做的飯長大的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.24,0:06:00.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}難吃得都要哭出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:08.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與我親近的話  媽媽也會病倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴原來是在為這個苦惱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:18.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽我說  觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得病什麼的我一點都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真要是得病了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我會感到高興
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:31.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那不正說明我和觀鈴變得親近了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:49.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剪多少合適
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.38,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}交給媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:19.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  那就剪成觀鈴看上去最可愛的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:24.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽的皺紋變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要我把你剪成寸頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呵呵  開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽很年輕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:31.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}以前學校進行公開授課的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:33.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其他人的媽媽都是中年人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.27,0:07:34.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我自己很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時你回答錯了問題哭了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:44.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道答案卻想出出風頭就舉手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那時媽媽大庭廣眾之下就來揍我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰讓你說那個「嘎哦」來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是管教
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:55.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}多虧了您觀鈴才能長這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:57.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:07:59.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}成長了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.15,0:08:02.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個口頭禪也不怎麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:12.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:19.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣倒是方便剪頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}得和這邊長短一致才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇！ 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:38.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這回另一邊又剪短了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.81,0:08:49.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}倒是剪得長短一致了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:04.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哇  變得非常短了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像變回小孩子了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}兩個人一起重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  現在起重新開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:25.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}V
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吶  夏日祭快開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:37.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不說我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:41.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想和媽媽一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:45.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那還用說 帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後  還想去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還沒有和媽媽一起去過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.91,0:09:54.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小觀鈴想去的地方還真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:58.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯  想和媽媽一起做很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  做很多有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.51,0:10:04.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓你的繪畫日記寫得滿滿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我記著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:12.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}永遠不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:18.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不懂你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼回事  觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:43.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼了  還困嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:56.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:02.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}忘記了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是說好了和媽媽一起努力的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:05.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對啊  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}媽媽去了很遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不用想那些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就是你的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:31.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從今天開始重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:35.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在讓你叫我媽媽那天到來以前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:37.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就叫我晴子阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我借來了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看啊  有了這個就能出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}腿很疼走不動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才借了這個輪椅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  我來推著你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:58.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一個人玩撲克牌更有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:01.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  兩個人一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到外邊曬曬太陽多舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:06.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}還有很多很多有趣的事可以做喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}風在吹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在吹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}艷陽高照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:20.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:23.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}知了嗡嗡地叫著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吵得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:26.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是麼  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:36.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:38.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我是你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:44.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你也知道這孩子無法生活在人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才把她送來這個寧靜的小鎮中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過看來是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:56.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你還不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她已經是我家的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:00.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經得到了你父母的允許
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:02.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我和你姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.72,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}覺得麻煩的時候送到我這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想起來時又要帶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.93,0:13:09.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神尾家就是這樣方便的地方嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:13.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不能眼睜睜地看著在你身邊生病的她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要在我面前講普通話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}聽得我好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}抱歉  嚷嚷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨… 嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:29.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直叫我媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:31.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}來  向晴子阿姨道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快  說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:39.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:40.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.84,0:13:44.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不要帶走觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:46.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}她一直是孤零零一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:47.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是誰的責任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不正是我們的責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以我才決定要一直陪在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:56.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}難道因為我們之間的矛盾你就要帶走她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:57.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我腦子不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道這話該怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:02.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過有一點可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比起你我更想和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:07.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那就問問她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:12.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今後也想和晴子阿姨生活在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}晴子阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:20.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}對  想和晴子阿姨繼續生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:21.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:23.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}敬介你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:24.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給我三天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果三天後這孩子說不想和我在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那我也就沒什麼可說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你帶走她我也毫無怨言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}求你了  敬介
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:41.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天能讓我們找回母女親情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:53.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}小觀鈴真的是非常喜歡恐龍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個是「慈母龍」（Maiasaura peeblesorum ）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}代表慈祥的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿  還真像我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:03.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個是「速龍（恐爪龍）」（Velociraptor）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:05.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}代表敏捷的小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:08.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哈  像敬介一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底誰才是小偷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:21.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:23.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過忍耐一會就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:26.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到了海邊應該會更涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:28.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我親手做的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:32.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我要回家
