Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:42.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那  阿姨就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}阿姨  可以留在這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經沒什麼可奢求的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:13.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}能和你在一起  哪怕只有一天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我所希望的僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天是和敬介約好的期限
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.87,0:18:34.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個呆子會再詢問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.69,0:18:39.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你則會回答想和他一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會說  不再想和我在一起了吧
