Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.10,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}分別前想帶這孩子去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.23,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.58,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}觀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:20.89,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.02,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是海喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.27,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.57,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好漫長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.61,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了我倆能一起來到海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.26,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底花了多少年的時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.34,AIR context 2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}原本可以將這麼美的景色看個夠的
